                "description": {
                    "value": "<p data-visibility=\"gm\"><strong>Trigger</strong> A living creature bearing <em>Hunger's Call</em> moves within 30 feet of the exit stairs;</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> Blood pounds in the targe's body as their heart races uncontrollably. The creature must attempt a <span data-pf2-check=\"will\" data-pf2-traits=\"arcane,death,fear,complex\" data-pf2-label=\"Resist Racing Blood DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"20\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Will</span> save, and the haunt then rolls initiative.</p>\n<div data-visibility=\"gm\"><hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The target is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Sickened]{Sickened 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The target is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Sickened]{Sickened 2}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> As failure, and the target's move speed is reduced by 10 for 1 minute.</p>\n</div>"
